'''基督新教'''，簡稱'''新教'''，源於[[16世紀|16世紀]]神學家[[馬丁·路德|馬丁·路德]]、[[約翰·加爾文|約翰·加爾文]]、[[烏利希·慈運理|烏利希·慈運理]]等人所領導的[[宗教改革|宗教改革]]運動，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lexico.com/definition/protestant|title=PROTESTANT - Meaning & Definition for UK English|website=Lexico.com by Oxford|access-date=2022-05-12|archive-date=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610061314/https://www.lexico.com/definition/protestant}}</ref>是[[基督教|基督教]][[西方教會|西方教會]]中[[天主教會|天主教會]]以外[[基督教派系|宗派]]的統稱，<ref name=CanadianEncyclopedia1999>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wR_-aSFyvuYC&pg=PA1920|title=''The Canadian Encyclopedia''|editor=Marsh, James H.|date=1999|page=1920|publisher=McClelland & Stewart Inc.|isbn=0771020996|access-date=2022-05-02|archive-date=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610061320/https://books.google.com/books?id=wR_-aSFyvuYC&pg=PA1920}}</ref><ref name=PSue1999>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wp959ngsh1QC&pg=PA12|title=''Christianity''|first=Sue|last=Penney|date=1999|page=12|publisher=Heinemann Educational Publishers|isbn=0435304771|access-date=2020-05-11|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323181126/https://books.google.com/books?id=wp959ngsh1QC&pg=PA12}}</ref>與[[天主教|天主教]]、[[東正教|東正教]]並列為基督宗教三大分支。<ref name=MNickens>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=_GoPEAAAQBAJ&pg=PT158|title=''A Survey of the History of Global Christianity''|first=Mark|last=Nickens|date=2020|page=158|publisher=B&H Academic|isbn=978-1-5359-8500-0|quote=Christianity roughly consists of three divisions: Catholic, Protestant and Orthodox.|access-date=2022-05-25|archive-date=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610072302/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=_GoPEAAAQBAJ&pg=PT158}}</ref>新教的核心教義為「[[因信稱義|因信稱義]]」，<ref>Luther, Martin (1537), Smalcald Articles, [https://bookofconcord.org/smalcald-articles/ii/first-and-chief-article/ Article I - First and Chief Article] {{Wayback|url=https://bookofconcord.org/smalcald-articles/ii/first-and-chief-article/ |date=20220502161648 }}</ref><ref>Holmes, D.L., ''A Brief History of the Episcopal Church'', pp2-3, "Called 'justification by grace through faith,' this central teaching of Protestantism is articulated in such hymns as 'A Mighty Fortress is Our God,' 'Ah, Holy Jesus,' and 'Just as I Am.'"</ref>強調[[基督|基督]]已經作出[[耶穌被釘十字架|犧牲]]為世人[[贖罪|贖罪]]，<ref name=AS46/>人是單單藉著信心<ref name=moitw-diff>{{cite web|url=http://religion.moi.gov.tw/Knowledge/Content?ci=2&cid=296|title=《基督新教》|author=曾祖漢|publisher=全國宗教資訊網|access-date=2022-05-27|quote=新教有別於天主教，可以從新教在某些教義和神學的前提上看得出來，馬丁·路德在公元1517年開始宗教改革的運動，他的神學思想起點源於個人的經歷，到底面對公義的神時，人要如何才能夠被接納呢？「因信稱義」（Justification through faith）是路德也是新教的關鍵教義，意思是因著信心的緣故，神把人當作義人（稱義），不是人本身有什麼值得討神喜悅的，而是公義的神在審判的時候不再看人的不完全，而只看到信心的對象，即耶穌基督，雖然世人都無法過一個完美的一生在神面前被稱為義，但是神的兒子耶穌基督過了完美的一生得著了「義」的地位，信徒只要藉著信靠耶穌基督，這個耶穌基督的義就被轉撥到我們身上，因此，神是因著耶穌基督的緣故，稱那些相信之人為義人。|archive-date=2016-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160720144659/http://religion.moi.gov.tw/Knowledge/Content?ci=2&cid=296}}</ref>而不是靠善行<ref name=SALEM7>南亞路德會，《信仰立場》，頁7：「人藉著信心（相信和接受耶穌基督為救主）便可得著這救恩。『你們得救是本乎恩，也因著信；這並不是出於自己，乃是上帝所賜的；也不是出於行為，免得有人自誇。』(弗2:8-9)」</ref><ref name=qa17580>WELS Topical Q&A: [https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20090927212902/https://www.wels.net/cgi-bin/site.pl?1518&cuTopic_topicID=19&cuItem_itemID=17580 Faith and Works]</ref>獲得上帝的[[得救|拯救]]。<ref name=twbp9>[https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20090926222403/http://www.wels.net/cgi-bin/site.pl?2617&collectionID=783&contentID=92109&shortcutID=30682 《我們所信》]，亞洲路德宗神學院翻譯事務社，頁9，「每個人藉着信領受這份禮物（以弗所書2:8,9），而非藉着他們的行為...不信的人將失去基督為他們贏取的赦罪（約翰福音8:24）。」</ref>新教以《[[聖經|聖經]]》為信仰之唯一權威，<ref name=solascriptura>WELS Topical Q&A: [https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20090927214527/https://www.wels.net/cgi-bin/site.pl?1518&cuTopic_topicID=39&cuItem_itemID=12132 Sola Scriptura], "many passages...state sola scriptura, such as Revelation 22:18-19. If we cannot add anything to the words of Scripture and we cannot take anything away from them, that is Scripture alone."</ref><ref name=scripturealone>{{cite web|url=http://www.salem.org.hk/5sola/02_1.html|title=唯獨聖經|publisher=南亞路德會|4=|access-date=2018-03-22|archive-date=2020-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218124357/http://www.salem.org.hk/5sola/02_1.html}}</ref>並且否定<ref name=QA-Peter>WELS Topical Q&A: [https://wels.net/faq/peter-the-first-pope/ Peter the first pope?] {{Wayback|url=https://wels.net/faq/peter-the-first-pope/ |date=20210303075420 }}</ref>天主教[[教皇制|教皇制]]，<ref name=ST337>巴刻，《簡明神學》，頁337，「當改教家們反對教皇制，並與羅馬天主教分道揚鑣時，他們需要決定什麼是真教會的標記。他們從聖經裏找到了答案，這標記有兩個標準：第一，肯忠實地傳講神道：其意為，受置疑的團體必須肯根據聖經，教導基督教福音的基要之道。」</ref><ref name=PJenkins>Jenkins, Paul (2014), [http://essays.wisluthsem.org:8080/bitstream/handle/123456789/7/Power%20and%20Primacy%20Paper.pdf?sequence=1&isAllowed=y ''The Relevance of Treatise on the Power and Primacy of the Pope for Today's Lutheran Pastor''] {{Wayback|url=http://essays.wisluthsem.org:8080/bitstream/handle/123456789/7/Power%20and%20Primacy%20Paper.pdf?sequence=1&isAllowed=y |date=20220516005331 }}, pp3-4</ref><ref name=JCalvin>[[約翰·加爾文|Calvin, John]], ''[[基督教要義|Institutes of the Christian Religion]]'' (Vol. 2), Translated by John Allen, Wipf & Stock, 2013, p335</ref>更相信所有信徒都[[普遍的祭司職分|具有祭司的身分]]。<ref name = "Encyclopedia of Protestantism">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=bW3sXBjnokkC&pg=PR11|title=''Encyclopedia of Protestantism''|first=J. Gordon|last=Melton|date=2018|page=11|publisher=Infobase Publishing|isbn=9780816069835|access-date=2018-03-23|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323181207/https://books.google.com/books?id=bW3sXBjnokkC&pg=PR11}}</ref>教內不同宗派在[[聖餐|聖餐觀]]等神學問題上持不同看法，<ref name="CSDixon">{{cite book|last=Dixon|first=C. Scott|title=''Protestants: A History from Wittenberg to Pennsylvania 1517-1740''|url={{Google books|xLBa5aO7fgQC|page=32|plainurl=yes}}|page=32}}</ref>但普遍遵循「[[五個唯獨|五個唯獨]]」原則。<ref name="fivesolae">{{cite web|url=http://www.salem.org.hk/5sola/01.html|title=五個唯獨：簡介|publisher=南亞路德會|access-date=2018-03-22|archive-date=2021-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322094617/http://www.salem.org.hk/5sola/01.html}}</ref><ref name="PECH">{{cite book|last1=Hindson|first1=Ed|editor1-last=Mitchell|editor1-first=Dan|title=''The Popular Encyclopedia of Church History: The People, Places, and Events that shaped Christianity''|page=277}}</ref><ref name="christianitydotcom">{{cite web|last1=Holcomb|first1=Justin|url=http://www.christianity.com/church/church-history/the-five-solas-of-the-protestant-reformation.html|title=''The Five Solas - Points from the past that should matter to you''|website=Christianity.com|access-date=2017-08-20|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117045026/http://www.christianity.com/church/church-history/the-five-solas-of-the-protestant-reformation.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在路德之前，已有多位宗教改革家嘗試改革甚至脫離天主教會，但最後直至路德的[[德意志宗教改革|德意志宗教改革]]才獲得成功。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=uw78AwAAQBAJ&pg=PA98|title=''Religious Thoughts''|first=James|last=Watson|date=2014|page=98|publisher=iUniverse|isbn=9781491737590|access-date=2018-03-22|archive-date=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610061513/https://books.google.com/books?id=uw78AwAAQBAJ&pg=PA98}}</ref>16世紀[[路德宗|路德宗]]信仰由[[德意志|德意志]]傳入[[丹麥|丹麥]]、[[挪威|挪威]]、[[瑞典|瑞典]]、[[芬蘭|芬蘭]]、[[拉脫維亞|拉脫維亞]]、[[愛沙尼亞|愛沙尼亞]]和[[冰島|冰島]]，<ref name=HistDictLuth>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Htz8M1Xlqi4C&pg=PA9|title=''Historical Dictionary of Lutheranism''|first1=Günther|last1=Gassmann|first2=Duane H.|last2=Larson|first3=Mark W.|last3=Oldenburg|date=4 April 2001|page=9|publisher=The Scarecrow Press, Inc.|isbn=0810839458|access-date=2018-03-22|archive-date=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610070110/https://books.google.com/books?id=Htz8M1Xlqi4C&pg=PA9}}</ref>另一位宗教改革家[[加爾文|加爾文]]的思想亦傳入[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]、[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]、[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]、[[瑞士|瑞士]]和[[法國|法國]]。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1asvyE-1DUkC&pg=PT19|title=''Calvinism''|first=Abraham|last=Kuyper|date=1899|page=19|publisher=Primedia E-launch LLC|isbn=9781622090457|access-date=2018-03-22|archive-date=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610070117/https://books.google.com/books?id=1asvyE-1DUkC&pg=PT19}}</ref>同期的[[英國國王|英國國王]][[亨利八世|亨利八世]]亦帶領當地教會脫離天主教體制，開展[[英格蘭宗教改革|英格蘭宗教改革]]。<ref name=HenryVIIILeague>McEntegart, Rory, ''Henry VIII, the League of Schmalkalden, and the English Reformation'', p14</ref>新教成功發展出其獨特文化，在[[教育|教育]]、[[人文|人文]]、[[科學|科學]]、[[政治|政治]]和社會秩序、[[經濟|經濟]]、[[藝術|藝術]]等領域為人類帶來重大貢獻。<ref name="Karl Heussi 1956 pp. 317–319">{{cite book|last1=Karl|first=Heussi|title=''Kompendium der Kirchengeschichte''|volume=11|publisher=Auflage|year=1956|location=Tübingen (Germany)|page=317-319, 325-326}}</ref>

「新教」之西方詞源[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]「protestatio」（「[[抗議|抗議]]」），是指[[1529年|1529年]][[神聖羅馬帝國|神聖羅馬帝國]]宣布路德為[[異端|異端]]之後所引起的強烈抗議，<ref name=PSue1999/>而漢譯「新教」是用作區別[[宗教改革|宗教改革]]前之“旧教”天主教。<ref name=moitw/>過往新教亦有「抗議派」、<ref name=Tong>唐凱麟（編），《西方倫理學名著提要》（下冊），頁61</ref>「抗羅宗」、<ref>{{Cite book | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=GJouDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA45 | author = 劉幸枝 | title = 《主護城傳奇：欽岑多夫伯爵與十八世紀摩拉維亞復興史》 | location = 台灣 | publisher = 橄欖出版 | date = 2009 | page = 45 | isbn = 9789866355455 | accessdate = 4/5/2022 | archive-date = 2022-06-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220610063604/https://books.google.com/books?id=GJouDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA45 }}</ref>「歸正教」、「復原教」、「更正教」、<ref name=CR39>''The Chinese Recorder'' (Vol. 39), American Presbyterian Mission Press, 1908, p157</ref><ref name=Ng>吳國傑，《拆壁重修：宗教改革縱橫談》，頁5</ref>「誓反教」<ref name=CheungSR>張信剛，《文明的地圖—一部絲綢之路的風雲史》（海外修訂版），頁54</ref>等別稱，現時[[漢語圈|漢語圈]]普遍直稱基督新教為「'''基督教'''」，羅馬天主教會為「天主教」，東正教會為「東正教」，並統稱眾基督信仰為「[[基督宗教|基督宗教]]」。<ref name=moitw>{{cite web|url=http://religion.moi.gov.tw/Knowledge/Content?ci=2&cid=296|title=《基督新教》|author=曾祖漢|publisher=全國宗教資訊網|access-date=2022-05-27|quote=廣泛的基督教包含了新教、天主教、東正教以及許多其中衍生的教派，狹義的基督教稱為新教，就是對應舊教（天主教），新教同時有許多的其他的名稱，每個名稱都代表著對天主教的區別和改革，因此新教也稱為[[抗羅宗|抗羅宗]]或[[更正教|更正教]]等等，而這個分裂的過程被稱為宗教改革運動。|archive-date=2016-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160720144659/http://religion.moi.gov.tw/Knowledge/Content?ci=2&cid=296}}</ref><ref name=hk>{{cite book|url=http://www.yearbook.gov.hk/2015/tc/pdf/C20.pdf|title=《香港年報》第二十章：宗教和風俗|access-date=2016-08-09|archive-date=2016-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820142419/http://www.yearbook.gov.hk/2015/tc/pdf/C20.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

有別於天主教和東正教，新教在全球教會組織上沒有單一架構或領導，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=matthew20:25-26&version=CUVMPT;TR1550|title=《馬太福音》二十章25-26節上|access-date=2022-05-12|quote=耶穌叫了他們來，說：「你們知道，外邦人有君王為主治理他們，有大臣操權管束他們。只是在你們中間不可這樣」|archive-date=2022-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220608062207/https://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=matthew20%3A25-26&version=CUVMPT%3BTR1550}}</ref><ref name=CommentaryMatthew>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4c4UAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA296|title=''The Pulpit Commentary: St. Matthew'' (Vol. 2)|editor=Spence, H.D.M.|date=1894|page=296|publisher=Kegan Paul, Trench, Trübner & Co. Ltd.|access-date=2022-05-27|archive-date=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610061614/https://books.google.com/books?id=4c4UAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA296}}</ref>教內主要宗派包括[[路德宗|路德宗]]、[[改革宗|改革宗]]、[[聖公會|聖公會]]、[[浸礼宗|浸礼宗]]、[[重洗派|重洗派]]、[[衛理公會|衛理公會]]、[[再臨宗|再臨宗]]、[[五旬宗|五旬宗]]等。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Ellwood|first1=R.S.|last2=Alles|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1pGbdI4L0qsC&pg=PA359|first2=G.D.|title=''The Encyclopedia of World Religions''|page=359|access-date=2022-04-04|archive-date=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610063608/https://books.google.com/books?id=1pGbdI4L0qsC&pg=PA359}}</ref>傳統新教宗派雖大多從天主教會中分離，但一些既不出自天主教，亦與[[歐洲|歐洲]]宗教改革沒有歷史淵源的教會及信徒，例如[[獨立教會|獨立教會]]和[[無連屬基督徒|無連屬基督徒]] (Unaffiliated Christians){{NoteTag|即沒有教會會籍或不屬任何宗派的信徒。<ref name=MJWM>Mandryk, J., Wall, M., 《萬國代禱手冊》, 頁383</ref>}}，也被視為基督新教。<ref name=RDWC2022>Anckar, Carsten (2022), ''Religion and Democracy: A Worldwide Comparison'', p103, "Wide definition of Protestantism...includes Protestants, Marginal Christians, Anglicans, Christian Independents, and unaffiliated Christians"</ref><ref name=TheFuture>{{cite book|last1=Johnstone|first1=Patrick|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=AVzFAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA115|title=''The Future of the Global Church: History，Trends and Possibilities''|page=115|access-date=2020-05-11|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323182159/https://books.google.com/books?id=AVzFAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA115|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="pew2011">{{cite web|url=http://www.pewforum.org/2011/12/19/global-christianity-traditions/|title=''Christian Traditions''|work=Pew Research Center|date=2011|quote=Independent Christians include denominations in sub-Saharan Africa that identify as independent from historically Protestant denominations, churches in China that are not affiliated with official religious associations and nondenominational churches in the United States.|access-date=2016-08-05|archive-date=2017-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170720010855/http://www.pewforum.org/2011/12/19/global-christianity-traditions/|dead-url=no}}</ref>現時全球約有10億新教徒，<ref name=IOsborn>{{cite book|last1=Osborn|first1=Ian|year=2008|title=''Can Christianity Cure Obsessive-Compulsive Disorder? A Psychiatrist Explores the Role of Faith in Treatment''|page=46|quote=Almost a billion Protestants in the present day owe their religious identity to Luther's insights.}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Pack|first1=David C.|year=2009|title=''Saturday Or Sunday: Which Is the Sabbath?''|page=8|quote=About 1 billion Protestants also observe Sunday.}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Simon|first1=E.|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/made-by-history/wp/2017/10/31/were-all-protestants-now/|title=''We're all Protestants now''|publisher=Washington Post|access-date=2020-05-03|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323181319/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/made-by-history/wp/2017/10/31/were-all-protestants-now/|dead-url=no}}</ref>包括6億多傳統宗派信徒、4億多獨立教會信徒和1億多無教會會籍信徒。<ref name="gordonconwell.edu">{{Cite journal |author=Gina A. Zurlo |author2=Todd M. Johnson |author3=Peter F. Crossing |url=https://www.gordonconwell.edu/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Zurlo-Johnson-Crossing-IBMR-2022-World-Christianity-and-Religions-2022-A-Complicated-Relationship.pdf |title=''World Christianity 